The Last of the Mohicans;;88;;93;;R;;The last members of a dying Native American tribe, the Mohicans -- Uncas (Eric Schweig), his father Chingachgook (Russell Means), and his adopted half-white brother Hawkeye (Daniel Day-Lewis) -- live in peace alongside British colonists. But when the daughters (Madeleine Stowe, Jodhi May) of a British colonel are kidnapped by a traitorous scout, Hawkeye and Uncas must rescue them in the crossfire of a gruesome military conflict of which they wanted no part: the French and Indian War.;;Romance,Drama,War,History,Adventure;;Michael Mann;;1992;;Daniel Day-Lewis,Madeleine Stowe,Russell Means,Eric Schweig,Jodhi May,Steven Waddington,Wes Studi,Maurice Roëves,Patrice Chéreau;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1040678-last_of_the_mohicans